<body>
    <header>
        <div class="hig">
            <h1>Text-Summarizer</h1>
            <p>MEAN // Machine Learning !!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section info">A summary is a text that is produced from one or more texts, that conveys important
            information in the original text, and it is of a shorter form. The goal of automatic text summarization is
            presenting the source text into a shorter version with meaningful semantics. The most important advantage
            of using a summary is it reduces the reading time.</div>
